~ exponential {
    ~ helper {
        $3 == 0 ?
            $4 :
            1 # $2 <= $1:
                ($1 @ helper $2, $3 - 1, $4 + 1) :
                $4
    }
    $1 @helper $2, $3, 1
}

"last parameter is a limit on the distribution size"
"example: 1 @exponential 2 1000 - an exponential distribution with chance 1/2 capped at 1000 entries"